	<div class = "container">
		<div class = "row">
			<br>
			<h1 style="text-align: center; color: white">How VolunTeach Works:</h1>
			<div class = "col-md-6">
				<p class = "bigger-txt"><strong style= "color: white">1) Propose</strong> a class that you would like to teach.<br><div style = "text-align:center"><%= image_tag "propose.png", size: "250x300", style: "border-radius: 5px"%></div></p>
				<p class = "bigger-txt"><strong style= "color:white">3) Message</strong> a school through our inbuilt inbox.<br><div style = "text-align:center"><%= image_tag "message.png", size: "400x300", style: "border-radius: 5px"%></div></p>
				<p class = "bigger-txt"><strong style= "color:white">5) Share</strong> what you're passionate about.<br><img src ="http://www.skillsportal.co.za/sites/default/files/company-images/Emergence%20Learning%20Hub/Many-people-chatting-about-everything-learning.jpg" style="height:300px; text-align:center; border-radius:5px"></p>
			</div>
			<div class = "col-md-6">
				<p class = "bigger-txt"><strong style= "color:white">2) Browse</strong> schools in need near you.<br><div style = "text-align:center"><%= image_tag "browse.png", size: "400x300", style: "border-radius: 5px"%></div></p>
				<p class = "bigger-txt"><strong style= "color:white">4) Teach and Inspire</strong> young people.<br><img src ="http://teach.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/matmed.jpg" style="height:300px text-align:center; border-radius:5px"></p>
				<p class = "bigger-txt"><strong style= "color:white">6) Make an impact</strong> in your community.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

